    "reviews": [
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-03",
        "text": "I could say a million positive things about Taylor. Not only is she an incredible photographer, but she is an incredible person. She is professional, personable, and makes you feel comfortable being in front of her camera (which can sometimes be uncomfortable for people). Taylor shot our engagement photos in Sedona and our wedding in Keystone, CO. She always scouts out great locations with incredible views and captures beautiful photos! She's always prepared with a plan A, B and C if necessary. One of my favorite qualities about Taylor is that she is so kind and makes you feel like you've known her for years!\n\nI would highly recommend Taylor as your photographer. She is not only passionate about photography, she is passionate about her clients and their vision!\n\nWe love you Taylor! Thank you for capturing the big important moments, as well as the little intimate moments from our big day."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2019-07",
        "text": "Taylor created a whole experience for us!! She met us in Iceland and travelled happily and peachy in close quaters with us for 12hrs and I have the pleasure to say I'd do it all over again in a heartbeat!! She's an amazing photographer with great vision and instructions. She won't leave ya hanging, she makes it fun, comfortable, and she goes above and beyond as a photographer and a person!!\nHighly recommended for any wedding, couple, or travel photography!\nWill be a returning client 😁"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2018-09",
        "text": "Taylor went above and beyond expectations for our wedding weekend in August. She wanted to be at every part of the wedding including the rehearsal dinner, the venue walkthrough, the ceremony rehearsal, etc. She made it a priority to get the to know us as well as all of our family and friends. She spent a day with us taking beautiful pre-wedding photos instead of engagement photos and included our pup with lots of love. She knows all of the best spots in Telluride to get the perfect pictures. On the wedding day she basically took over as the wedding coordinator and made sure we were staying on time and where we were when we needed to be leading up to the ceremony. She is a genuinely happy and nice person who is passionate about what she does. We would not have done anything differently and she made our wedding weekend and day so perfect! The pictures we have seen so far are gorgeous! Thank you Taylor!!"
      }
    ]
  },
